    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been thinking about what you said... about the doctors just prolonging things. it feels like i'm just trapped in this waiting room. if i can't stop the decline, i at least wish i could decide how it ends. wouldn't it be better to have some control over the exit, rather than just letting it happen to me?",
